      '<strong>Confirm the licensing pathway before you sign the lease.</strong> Whether you need a certificate of need, which licence class applies and what plan review requires can change the space, the build cost and the timeline entirely.',
      '<strong>Submit credentialing files complete or not at all.</strong> An incomplete file does not start the clock — it goes to the back of the queue when it is corrected, and that single administrative slip is the most common cause of a delayed opening.',
      '<strong>Design for plan review, not just for the builder.</strong> Health authority plan review has specific requirements on room sizes, sinks, pressure relationships and finishes, and a redesign after a review comment costs far more than getting it right first.',
